- Many of these KPIs have global_p95 == 0 and max_value_in_window == 0. Because P95 is zero, the condition value >= P95 is trivially true (or ambiguous for zero-valued metrics), causing every point to be counted as a breach. Examples with zero P95 include fs read/write seconds, many fs/read counts, cpu cfs throttling counters, load average, etc.
